title: [SOLVED]820-3435-b no image after liquid damage
message: There is backlight, there is chime but no image on screen. What should I check?

title: [SOLVED]820-3435-b no image after liquid damage
message: If there is backlight there must be an image. Either bad LCD or bad SSD that hangs the system.

title: [SOLVED]820-3435-b no image after liquid damage
message: SSD was holding it. It went faulty. Solved.Thanks.
